==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''parallelogram''' ({{plural}} '''parallelograms''')

#{{geometry}} A [[convex]] [[quadrilateral]] in which each pair of [[opposite]] edges are [[parallel]] and of equal length.

